  "text": "Whatever the employed techniques (with contact or not), and the environment (in air, liquid or vacuum) [CITATION_1] , due to specific mechanical and physical laws which govern the micro-world, micromanipulation systems often suffer from a lack of reproducibility. That is why micromanipulation tasks need complex and robust control based on sensor feedback.",
